    "description": "Three years ago, three beasts fell from the sky.\n\nKing Qin of the Western Hill made a contract with one of them and swept through the six kingdoms to unify the Western Hill.\n\nWu Jiu of the Southern Desert made a contract with the other and then he swept through the nineteen sects of the Southern Desert, reaching the peak.\n\nSun Changming also made a contract with one of them, yet three years passed without any change.\n\nHowever, he will soon discover that the little toothed fish he caught three years ago is the greatest blessing of his life!\n\nUnstoppable!",
